(42, 16, 16, 43, 1, 45, 45, 'the law and the prophets', 'Connection of Law and Prophets', 'Both passages emphasize the role of the law and the prophets in relation to Jesus. Luke 16:16 mentions the law and the prophets, while John 1:45 refers to Moses in the law and the prophets as writing about Jesus.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
