(42, 16, 17, 42, 21, 33, 33, NULL, 'Connection of Endurance of Words', 'Both passages emphasize the permanence of divine words in contrast to the transience of heaven and earth. Luke 16:17 asserts the unbreakable nature of the law, while Luke 21:33 highlights that Jesus'' words will endure beyond the physical realm.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
